{"type":"message","id":"578f45d9","parentId":"5c1db791","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:33:31.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The deep status shows everything is working. Let me compile a summary for Bobby:\n\n- Gateway: ✅ Running (pid 29665)\n- Node service: ✅ Running (pid 4359)\n- Telegram: ✅ OK (all 10 accounts connected)\n- Sessions: 439 active\n- Heartbeat: 30m for main agent, others disabled\n- Security warnings: 7 warnings (mostly about exec security and allowInsecureAuth)\n\nEverything looks good. Let me give Bobby a clean summary.","thinkingSignature":"6a1cd45268b182c805ae479fba0013708873c0e6337086942c11ebca6fb4f89b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**OpenClaw Status Update** ✅\n\n**Core Services**\n- Gateway: ✅ Running (pid 29665, loopback)\n- Node service: ✅ Running (pid 4359)\n- Dashboard: ✅ http://127.0.0.1:18789/\n\n**Channels**\n- Telegram: ✅ OK — 10 accounts connected\n\n**Sessions**\n- 439 total active sessions\n- Current: MiniMax-M2.7, 22% context used\n\n**Heartbeat**\n- Main agent: 30 min intervals ✅\n- Sub-agents: disabled (expected)\n\n**Security Warnings** (7 total — non-critical)\n- `allowInsecureAuth` enabled — safe since gateway is loopback-only\n- `exec security=full` — known, acceptable for your setup\n- All others are standard hardening suggestions\n\n**Summary:** Everything is running properly. No action needed. 🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1745,"output":289,"cacheRead":39808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777685601722,"responseId":"06448761b823ad00cd80dd8f85992a6c"}}
