lletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md\\n- Apply Gmail labels: gog gmail labels add <msg_id> '<LabelName>' --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram summary to 8212808444:\\n```\\n📬 NEW MAIL (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n```\\n\\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\\n\\nSTEP 7: If no new emails, send a simple confirmation: \\\"✅ Email check done — no new emails\\\" to confirm the cron ran.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false,\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1776715097337,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 549742,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776716315644\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 15,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 15,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"720739ac-4722-437b-8271-b7c1189c905c\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    },\n    \"3f20d0fb-bb39-4216-a3a2-d87613e075f4\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> last\",\n      \"detail\": \"last -> no route, will fail-closed: Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>\"\n    },\n    \"e63a926f-487e-4bbc-a626-cbf21b1b8670\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> telegram:telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"resolved from last, session agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\"\n  