{"type":"message","id":"79e002b6","parentId":"a5f7a459","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:35:21.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby asked two questions:\n1. Why so many active sessions and what does it mean?\n2. Confirm we don't need the MC watchdog\n\n**On sessions:** The 439 sessions is a cumulative count over time — session stores are created for each cron run, each agent interaction, etc. They're cleaned up weekly by the \"Weekly Session Cleanup\" cron. Most of these are old compacted sessions. Not a problem.\n\n**On MC Watchdog:** It's already disabled (`enabled: false`) in the cron list. It was the watchdog cron job that was failing. Since MC server runs as a LaunchAgent now (auto-start, auto-restart), the watchdog isn't needed. I can confirm it's already disabled.\n\n\nI'll clean up that memory file and confirm both points with Bobby — the sessions are just historical artifacts from the weekly cleanup, and the watchdog was already disabled so there's nothing to do there.","thinkingSignature":"7aa5d2c3f924a7f844372ba22dd80aebd926adc81407c20eace42ccb010d73c9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Sessions:** 439 sounds like a lot but it's not alarming — these are **cumulative session stores** from cron jobs, agent interactions, sub-agents etc. over time. Most get auto-compacted into summaries. The \"Weekly Session Cleanup\" cron runs every Sunday at 3 AM to prune them. So it's a slow drip of historical sessions that gradually get cleaned. Nothing broken.\n\n**MC Watchdog:** Already **disabled** in the cron list (I can see it there, `enabled: false`). And since MC server runs as a permanent LaunchAgent now (auto-starts on boot, auto-restarts on crash), the watchdog isn't needed anymore. \n\nWant me to delete the watchdog cron entirely and remove the memory file about it?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6673,"output":332,"cacheRead":42240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777685711131,"responseId":"064487cf73336a0b52c596600964241e"}}
