{"type":"message","id":"dd870c54","parentId":"a6aec0fe","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:58:46.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the cover-page.html title tag.\n","thinkingSignature":"1c5b694ec93da41a64793643fae0d7ad9f913b826fc51a505103fe74ea0c3a3b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nDone! Cover now has **3 clean lines:**\n\n```\n     🤖🦞\n  The OpenClaw Playbook\nBuild Your First AI Automation in 30 Minutes\n         (No Coding Required)\n```\n\nRefresh Safari to see the updated layout. Let me know if you want the font bigger or the spacing adjusted!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":203,"output":79,"cacheRead":66656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66938,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777687124759,"responseId":"06448d54d9f81037a6b10bc0da41a4e3"}}
