{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_251---6d04dc6a-1de7-4127-b109-c066601ebece.jpg (image/jpeg) | /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_251---6d04dc6a-1de7-4127-b109-c066601ebece.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n  \"message_id\": \"24266\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-01 22:03 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nplease confirm with me that this looks good and you approve of how it looks. then i will continue reading and we can continue to work through this openclaw guide","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"cc16d61d","parentId":"310059c9","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:04:35.049Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"4d170fbf","parentId":"cc16d61d","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:04:46.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is showing me a screenshot of the updated cover. Let me analyze the image.\n","thinkingSignature":"6814d54200fd80928adaa1e7c86e2eec31e80f65be44de40a2b44634b71e9767"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c3nprkvh3ucf_1","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_251---6d04dc6a-1de7-4127-b109-c066601ebece.jpg","prompt":"Describe the full cover page layout in detail - the title arrangement, subtitle placement, tagline, colors, spacing, and overall visual appearance."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66977,"output":113,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777687475049,"responseId":"06448eb437081ffef8e9c9df63e2a47e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"84ed1352","parentId":"4d170fbf","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:06:52.082Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c3nprkvh3ucf_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The cover page for \"The OpenClaw Playbook\" features a clean, modern, and high-tech aesthetic, utilizing a dark color palette with vibrant accents to create a professional digital-product appearance.\n\n### **Background and Overall Aesthetic**\n*   **Colors:** The primary background is a deep navy or midnight blue.\n*   **Texture:** A subtle, dark blue grid pattern (reminiscent of graph paper or blueprinting) covers the entire background, adding a technical, structured feel.\n*   **Accents:** A thin, solid gold vertical line runs down the far left edge of the page, providing a sharp contrast and a sense of \"premium\" branding. The bottom of the image features a subtle horizontal division, creating a \"floor\" effect.\n\n### **Header Elements**\n*   **Edition Tag:** At the top center, a small rectangular badge with rounded corners and a gold border contains the text \"2026 EDITION\" in a small, capitalized gold font.\n*   **Iconography:** Directly below the edition tag are two centered emojis: a classic robot head and a red lobster. These serve as a visual shorthand for the brand name \"OpenClaw.\"\n\n### **Title Arrangement**\n*   **The Main Title:** The title is the central focus, stacked in two lines of bold, sans-serif typography. \n    *   The top line reads \"**The OpenClaw**\" where \"The\" is in white and \"OpenClaw\" is in a striking gold. \n    *   The second line reads \"**Playbook**\" in large, prominent white text.\n*   **Spacing:** There is significant \"breathing room\" (negative space) surrounding the title, ensuring it is the first thing the eye gravitates toward.\n\n### **Subtitles and Taglines**\n*   **Primary Tagline:** Immediately below the title is the phrase \"Build Your First AI Automation in 30 Minutes\" in a medium-sized, light-grey sans-serif font.\n*   **Secondary Tagline:** Below the first, the parenthetical phrase \"(No Coding Required)\" is centered in a bright gold font, highlighting a key selling point of the product.\n\n### **Author Attribution Section**\n*   **Layout:** Located in the lower third of the page is a semi-transparent, dark blue horizontal capsule with rounded corners.\n*   **Content:** On the left side of this capsule is a circular gold badge containing the initials \"**BG**\" in navy. To the right of the badge, the name \"**Bobby G.**\" is written in white bold text, followed by the smaller sub-caption in light grey uppercase letters: \"BUILT FROM A REAL WORLD USER FOR REAL WORLD USE.\"\n\n### **Footer/Status Indicators**\n*   **Layout:** At the very bottom, three sets of data are arranged horizontally.\n*   **Visuals:** Large gold numbers are stacked above smaller, light-grey capitalized labels.\n    *   **10** (SECTIONS)\n    *   **7** (COMPLETE)\n    *   **3** (COMING SOON)\n*   **Purpose:** This gives the layout a \"dashboard\" feel, communicating progress and scope to the viewer.\n\n### **Visual Appearance Summary**\nThe overall layout is meticulously centered and balanced. The use of gold against a dark navy background creates a \"luxury tech\" feel, while the generous spacing and clear hierarchy of information make the page easy to navigate and highly professional."}],"details":{"model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_251---6d04dc6a-1de7-4127-b109-c066601ebece.jpg","attempts":[{"provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.5","error":"image description timed out after 1ms | image description timed out after 1ms"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777687612081}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f14e59c","parentId":"84ed1352","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:07:05.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cover looks good! The title layout is now clean with:\n- \"The OpenClaw\" (white + gold) + \"Playbook\" (white) on two lines - the subtitle flows nicely below\n- \"Build Your First AI Automation in 30 Minutes\" in light grey\n- \"(No Coding Required)\" in bright gold\n\nThis is much cleaner than before. I approve of how it looks.\n","thinkingSignature":"d323ff57ff3077077917f03a7214c57132ea88a63832f53098429e6e80dbc0d1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYes Bobby, **I approve this.** ✅\n\nThe title looks clean and professional now:\n\n- **\"The OpenClaw Playbook\"** — white + gold, bold, easy to read\n- **\"Build Your First AI Automation in 30 Minutes\"** — light grey, flows as one line\n- **\"(No Coding Required)\"** — gold, pops, underlines the value prop\n\nThe gold accents on dark navy = premium feel. Stats at the bottom (\"10 Sections / 7 Complete / 3 Coming Soon\") is a nice touch — sets expectations.\n\nGo ahead and read through the rest. Once you're done, let me know what changes or improvements you want to make!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6456,"output":226,"cacheRead":61568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68250,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777687612084,"responseId":"06448f412950bf8dd05facb434b6b41f"}}
