te\\n\\n• Core concepts: Sessions, Skills, Agents, Memory, Cron, Model/Provider\\n• Note: Agent roster listed (Dean, Emmy, Finn, etc.) — inside-baseball but fits a personal-use guide\\n\\nSection 7 ✅ Complete — BUT transitions into Draft territory\\n\\n• Morning Brief Skill template explanation\\n• Ends with [Attached as separate file: Morning-Brief-Skill-Template.md] then DRAFT notices for sections 8-10\\n\\nSection 8 ✅ Complete\\n\\n• 6 real-world workflows (YouTube pipeline, content repurposing, multi-agent ops, etc.)\\n• References \\\"Alex Finn\\\" — sounds like a real case study Bobby is citing\\n• Strong closing line: \\\"Master one, add the next...\\\"\\n\\nSection 9 ✅ Complete\\n\\n• 6 advanced techniques (Reverse Prompting, Heartbeat Trick, Memory Flush…[truncated]\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"3f581022","parentId":"038a383b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:44:49.827Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"aad4519d","parentId":"3f581022","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:45:05.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to tackle these issues one by one. Let me prioritize what should be done first.\n\nLooking at the issues:\n1. Remove all the `*More sections coming soon...*` placeholder text - this is the most widespread issue across sections 1-6 (sections 7-10 already have DRAFT notices)\n2. Check other sections for €100M reference\n3. Section 7 ends with file reference - needs proper closing\n4. Verify Section 10 content\n5. \"Alex Finn\" reference in Section 8\n\nThe first logical issue to tackle is probably the most impactful and most widespread - fixing the placeholder endings. Sections 1-6 all have the same placeholder at the end. Let me tackle that first.\n\n\nI should start with removing the placeholder endings from sections 1-6 since that's the most repetitive issue across the guide. But I need to know what Bobby actually wants as the closing for each section before I can replace it with actual content. Let me ask him which fix he'd like to prioritize first.\n","thinkingSignature":"9cb889c409432700e08a3b0ecd48588990cdd7b7c4d4835282b4ee549fdcc413"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**The placeholder endings** — removing `*More sections coming soon...*` from Sections 1-6. That's the first fix since it touches 6 sections and is the most obvious sign the guide isn't finished.\n\nWant me to start there? I'll replace each one with a proper closing line that actually fits the section. I'll show you each one before I apply it."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83691,"output":288,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84171,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777689889827,"responseId":"064498227aae2f81d6bb1d2f8cb8e5d2"}}
