{"type":"message","id":"7e6c93b3","parentId":"dbf35ce7","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:59:50.157Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gbct6ksp0o1y_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"     DRAFT PAGE: SECTION 10\n     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->\n<div class=\"draft-page\">\n  <div class=\"section-accent-bar\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"draft-header\">\n    <div class=\"draft-section-num\">Section 10</div>\n    <div class=\"draft-title\">My Daily<br>Workflow</div>\n    <div class=\"draft-subtitle\">A full breakdown of Bobby's daily OpenClaw-powered routine</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"draft-note\">\n    <div class=\"icon\">📋</div>\n    <div class=\"text\">This section is being written.<br>Full content coming soon.</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h3>What to expect:</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>A real walkthrough of what a day looks like with OpenClaw running your life</li>\n    <li>5:30 AM Morning Brief — what it includes and why</li>\n    <li>7 AM Morning Check-In — today + next 3 days + focus for the day</li>\n    <li>12 PM Midday Check-In — urgent items, pending, updates</li>\n    <li>5 PM Evening Wrap-Up — tomorrow preview, tonight tasks, day recap</li>\n    <li>9 PM Zyrtec reminder — simple but it keeps me consistent</li>\n    <li>10:26 PM Nightly Intel — cash position update every night</li>\n    <li>How all the pieces work together as a system</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <div class=\"section-footer\">\n    <p>Section 10 — My Daily Workflow 🔨 In Progress</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777690790157}}
